name: Traditional House #6B - Bale Tani
description: It's a pixel sprite 120x120 upscale to 1200x1200 of traditional house from West Nusa Tenggara, Indonesia. You can see this building in Sade Village, Lombok, West Nusa Tenggara. Bale Tani is one of the traditional houses that you can see in Sade Village, it's used as a place to live by the people there.
